openmediavault-dropbox-backup (1.0.1) stable; urgency=low

  * Fix backup schedule: hourly/daily/weekly selection now generates a
    systemd timer drop-in (previously always ran daily at 02:00)
  * Fix failure reporting: rclone errors now mark the backup as failed
    instead of success
  * Fix systemd sandboxing that prevented rclone from writing to the
    backup destination and refreshing its OAuth token
  * Add "Run Backup Now" button with live output to the workbench UI
  * Remove unused RPC methods (startAuth, getAuthStatus, unlinkAccount,
    getBackupStatus)
  * Replace placeholder homepage/documentation URLs

 -- Gabe Burke <gabeburke@gmail.com>  Sat, 04 Jul 2026 10:00:00 -0500

openmediavault-dropbox-backup (1.0.0) stable; urgency=low

  * Complete rewrite for OpenMediaVault 7.x
  * Renamed from openmediavault-dropbox to openmediavault-dropbox-backup
  * Changed to one-way backup (Dropbox to local)
  * Replaced Dropbox daemon with rclone for sync
  * OAuth authentication via rclone (no Dropbox app registration needed)
  * Added scheduled backups via systemd timer
  * Modern YAML-based workbench UI
  * Selective folder sync support

 -- Gabe Burke <gabeburke@gmail.com>  Sat, 14 Dec 2024 10:00:00 -0500

